{"tid":907554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得而家新一代MK大致可以分成三類","createTime":"2018-11-19T01:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T01:27:42.000Z","uid":208362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"330aca8abecab24d148f21b3c1b32bf11c3fce4f","tid":907554,"uid":208362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:22:32.000Z","msg":"第一種係屋村MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用ig多 啲post遮住個樣 好鍾意用歌詞做caption 長期都好抑鬱咁 扮曬有故事 新一代嘅會玩抖音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通常著潮牌(Aape,Champion,thrasher)<br />\n男嘅個頭會染到五光十色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女嘅通常一係著啲好短嘅運動褲 一係就露半pat嘅牛仔褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夜晚會成班聚係屋邨天台,籃球場,M記<br />\n會成日上人屋企打麻雀打牌 MK妹易手次數極高 十分淫亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n值得一提嘅係啲肥mk唔知點解特別多女 仲要質素ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二種係圍村MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢種MK屋企通常係撈偏 多數係圍村仔<br />\n好多呢種mk仔條嘅女幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通常有紋身 一樣鍾意將個頭染到五光十色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鍾意著以前興嘅潮牌 部分會有黑底<br />\n整體嚟講比較貼近以前嘅古惑仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三種係名校MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚴格嚟講 佢哋唔可以算係MK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過佢哋鍾意圍威喂 落bar<br />\n好鍾意搞埋啲小圈子是非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲女十個有九個行偽abc風<br />\n表面上冇乜嘢 其實私底下一樣十分淫亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上好多行為同屋邨MK無異<br />\n大個咗玩ocamp做on9嘢嘅主要就喺呢班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50c41fe5832d2d40888235537448fa98ae48d75","tid":907554,"uid":208362,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:27:42.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以補充啲圖 尤其係MK妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}